Created The Repo For learning.
How to create basic Cli with golang cobra

# INSTALLATION
Download the source code from the release tags
go get github.com/spf13/cobra
go build cli.go

cli  
#USAGE
Welcome Time Series

Usage:
  cli [command]

Available Commands:
  create      To Create the AWS Cloudformation Json Template
  day         Displays the Current local Day
  fact        Determines the factorial of the element n
  fib         Prints the Fibonacci of the elements
  help        Help about any command
  month       Displays the Current month of the Year
  time        Displays the current local time in 24-hour format
  zone        Displays the Current Local Time Zone

Flags:
  -h, --help   help for cli
   

Flags:
  -h, --help   help for cli

Below Command Displays the date of the month
cli day 
Below Command Displays month of the year
cli month 
Below Commands Displays the local time in 24-hour format
cli time 
Below Commands Displays the local time zone
cli zone 
Below Commands Create a autoscaling EC2 Json file
cli create
Below command creates the factorial of a number
cli fact number(8)
Below command creates the Fibonacci series of a number
cli fib number(5)